              <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:24px;color:${GlobalStyles.secondaryTextColor.color};margin-top:0;margin-bottom:10px;">In any event, the purchase of smartphone applications published by YBHive does not in any case give access to Paid Services without the purchase of a Subscription.</p>
