              <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:24px;color:${GlobalStyles.secondaryTextColor.color};margin-top:0;margin-bottom:10px;"><strong>8.1.1&nbsp;</strong>To use the Services, the Member or Subscriber must have the skills, equipment and software necessary for use of the Internet or the mobile applications of the Services. YBHive has security measures in place in connection with the use of the Services. However, the Member or Subscriber acknowledges that, due to the nature and limitations of the Internet, YBHive cannot warrant that any connection to the Internet or mobile applications will be completely secure.</p>
