              <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:24px;color:${GlobalStyles.secondaryTextColor.color};margin-top:0;margin-bottom:10px;"><strong>8.1.6&nbsp;</strong>The operation of the Services may be interrupted temporarily due to maintenance, updates or technical improvements, or to update the content and/or the way it is presented. If possible, YBHive will notify its Members and Subscribers before any maintenance operations or updates which may impact the Services.</p>
